About this app

Discover a simpler way to operate with your bank
The new Banco Patagonia application allows you to operate through your cell phone anytime, anywhere, with a simple and modern design.
You can access with the same username / document and password as in Patagonia eBank Personas and carry out the following operations:
* MODE
* Check balances and latest movements.
* Transfers between own and third party accounts
* Services pay.
* Payment of Cards, consultation of balances and expiration dates.
* Investments.
* Request and consultation of Loans.
* Subscription to messages and alerts.



In addition, you will be able to consult the savings and benefits, branches and nearest ATMs or contact us without having to enter your account.

Patagonia Móvil can use your telephone number in order to provide greater
security in your transactions.

Learn more about Patagonia Móvil at:
http://www.bancopatagonia.com.ar/personas/patagonia-movil.shtml
